                                AFFILIATIONS
     The Medical Center is affiliated with Henry Ford Hospital System in
    Detroit for rotations in urology. Other residents and students rotate
       in ophthalmology and podiatry. Students in psychiatry, clinical
   psychology, and dentistry also complete rotations at Togus. Additional
      affiliations include a variety of programs with University of New
     England, University of Rhode Island, University of North Carolina,
    University of Maine/Orono and Augusta Campuses, Southern and Central
        Maine Technical Colleges, Northeastern University, College of
            Osteopathic Medicine, and Touro College among others.

                               AUTHORIZED BEDS
   167 Authorized/Operating Beds: 67 - Medical/Surgical/Mental Health and
                             100 - Nursing Home

