                              HOURS OF SERVICE
   Administrative hours of operation are Monday through Friday, 8:00 a.m.
      to 4:30 p.m. Urgent/Emergent care may be obtained 24 hours a day.
                 Pharmacy hours of operation are as follows:

     Outpatient - Monday through Friday 8:00 a.m to 5:30 p.m.

     Inpatient - Monday through Saturday 8:00 a.m. to 7:00 p.m.
